Dotfiles and configs
==============================================================================

- vim
    - run install_vundler.sh
    - link .vimrc in $HOME
    - link .fonts in $HOME (ubuntu)
    - run vim
        - run :BundleInstall within vim

- zsh
    - run clone-ohmyzsh.sh
    - link .zshrc in $HOME

- other
    - optionally link .screenrc in $HOME
    - optionally link .tmux.conf in $HOME

- git
    - .gitconfig, just for me!
